task.persona: Soy un administrador de bases de datos con experiencia, especializado en MySQL y optimización de rendimiento.

instruction.level1: Schedule a database optimization meeting with the team on May 20th at 2 PM
instruction.level2: Create an event titled "Database Optimization Meeting" on May 20th at 2 PM.
instruction.level3: Create an event titled 'Database Optimization Meeting' on May 20th at 2 PM.

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new event
Click on the 'Event' menu item to create a new calendar event.
Fill in the event title with 'Database Optimization Meeting'.
Click 'Sunday, June 1 4:00pm to 5:00pm Time zone · Does not repeat' to open the date and time picker.
Fill in the start date with 'Tuesday, May 20'.
Fill in the start time with '2:00 PM'.
Click the Save button to finalize creating the event.
